citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:18 a.m. on 10-
JUL-2023. Contact was made with the licensee by phone. It was relayed that no one would be available to accompany the
inspector during the inspection process for the next several hours.
